Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-crewai`, instrumenting the `crewai`
framework: `Crew.kickoff` / `Crew.kickoff_async` (workflow spans),
`Agent.execute_task` (agent spans), and `BaseTool.run` (tool spans),
emitting standard GenAI semantic conventions (`gen_ai.*`) via
`opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
